</div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl border border-outline-variant max-w-[240px] animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 400ms;">
<p class="text-primary font-bold text-2xl">98%</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Lulusan melanjutkan ke jenjang pendidikan tinggi Islam ternama.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Alur Pendaftaran -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="bg-pattern absolute inset-0"></div>
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 relative z-10">
<div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-anim transition-all-custom">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Alur Pendaftaran Lengkap</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">Proses seleksi kami dirancang untuk memastikan keselarasan antara visi sekolah dengan kebutuhan serta potensi calon santri.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- Step 1 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2 scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" data-icon="edit_note">edit_note</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-on-surface">1. Mengisi Formulir</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Pendaftaran dilakukan secara daring melalui portal resmi kami. Pastikan data diri dan pilihan program studi sudah benar sebelum disimpan.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 2 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2 scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" data-icon="support_agent">support_agent</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-on-surface">2. Konsultasi</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Sesi tanya jawab khusus antara tim admin dengan orang tua untuk menyamakan visi pendidikan dan menjelaskan kurikulum Tarbiyah Sunnah.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 3 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2 scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" data-icon="visibility">visibility</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-on-surface">3. Observasi</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Pemantauan interaksi dan adaptasi calon santri di lingkungan sekolah untuk melihat kesiapan belajar serta minat bakat mereka.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 4 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2 scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 400ms;">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" data-icon="forum">forum</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-on-surface">4. Wawancara</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Pertemuan mendalam bersama pimpinan pondok untuk membahas kesiapan santri dan komitmen orang tua dalam mendukung proses pendidikan.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 5 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2 scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 500ms;">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" data-icon="campaign">campaign</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-on-surface">5. Pengumuman</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Hasil seleksi akan diumumkan melalui dashboard akun pendaftaran dan email resmi. Keputusan tim penguji bersifat final.</p>
</div>
<!-- Step 6 -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all group hover:-translate-y-2 scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 600ms;">
<div class="size-14 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl" data-icon="task_alt">task_alt</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-on-surface">6. Daftar Ulang</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Penyelesaian administrasi keuangan dan pengumpulan berkas fisik dokumen sebagai syarat sah menjadi santri resmi.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Jadwal & Biaya Section -->
<section class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-20 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
<!-- Documents & Requirements -->
<div class="space-y-10">
<div class="space-y-4 scroll-anim transition-all-custom">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-primary">Persyaratan Dokumen</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Pastikan Anda menyiapkan berkas digital (PDF/JPG) untuk proses unggah saat pengisian formulir.</p>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-surface-container rounded-lg scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="description">description</span>
<div>
<p class="font-bold text-on-surface">Identitas Diri</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Fotokopi Akta Kelahiran, Kartu Keluarga (KK), dan KTP Orang Tua.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-surface-container rounded-lg scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="school">school</span>
<div>
<p class="font-bold text-on-surface">Riwayat Pendidikan</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Fotokopi Rapor 2 tahun terakhir dan Ijazah (jika sudah ada).</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-surface-container rounded-lg scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="account_box">account_box</span>
<div>
<p class="font-bold text-on-surface">Pas Foto Terbaru</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Ukuran 3x4 (Background Merah) dengan pakaian formal dan sopan.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-5 bg-surface-container rounded-lg scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 400ms;">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="health_and_safety">health_and_safety</span>
<div>
<p class="font-bold text-on-surface">Surat Sehat</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Surat keterangan sehat dari dokter atau puskesmas setempat.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Important Dates Table -->
<div class="bg-primary p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-xl text-on-primary space-y-8 scroll-anim transition-all-custom">
<h2 class="font-headline-md">Jadwal Penting</h2>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex justify-between border-b border-primary-container pb-4">
<div>
<p class="font-bold">Gelombang 1</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-primary-container">Pendaftaran &amp; Unggah Berkas</p>
</div>
<p class="text-right font-medium">1 Okt - 30 Des 2023</p>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between border-b border-primary-container pb-4 relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-container/20 -translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex w-full justify-between">
<div>
<p class="font-bold flex items-center gap-2">Tes Seleksi <span class="size-2 bg-secondary rounded-full animate-pulse-slow"></span></p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-primary-container">Online &amp; Offline</p>
</div>
<p class="text-right font-medium">15 Jan 2024</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between border-b border-primary-container pb-4">
<div>
<p class="font-bold">Pengumuman Kelulusan</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-primary-container">Hasil Seleksi Akhir</p>
</div>
<p class="text-right font-medium">30 Jan 2024</p>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between border-b border-primary-container pb-4">
<div>
<p class="font-bold">Daftar Ulang</p>
<p class="text-sm text-on-primary-container">Administrasi &amp; Seragam</p>
</div>
<p class="text-right font-medium">1 - 15 Feb 2024</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary-container p-6 rounded-lg">
<p class="text-sm italic">"Barangsiapa yang menempuh jalan untuk mencari ilmu, maka Allah akan mudahkan baginya jalan menuju surga." (HR. Muslim)</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-high py-20">
<div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6">
<div class="text-center mb-12 scroll-anim transition-all-custom">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-primary">Pertanyaan Sering Diajukan (FAQ)</h2>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<details class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg border border-outline-variant group scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="">Berapa batas usia minimal untuk mendaftar?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="faq-content">
<div class="faq-inner px-6 pb-6 text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
                                Untuk jenjang Sekolah Dasar (Elementary), calon santri minimal berusia 6 tahun pada bulan Juli tahun ajaran baru. Untuk jenjang di atasnya, wajib menyertakan ijazah dari jenjang sebelumnya.
                            </div>
</div>
</details>
<details class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg border border-outline-variant group scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="">Apakah tersedia kelas Trial (Percobaan)?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="faq-content">
<div class="faq-inner px-6 pb-6 text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
                                Ya, kami menyediakan Open House dan Trial Class selama satu hari penuh di setiap bulan November. Silakan hubungi admin kami untuk reservasi kuota.
                            </div>
</div>
</details>
<details class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg border border-outline-variant group scroll-anim transition-all-custom" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer font-bold text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="">Bagaimana sistem asrama di Tarbiyah Sunnah?</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="faq-content">
<div class="faq-inner px-6 pb-6 text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
                                Asrama dikelola dengan pengawasan ketat dari Musyrif/Musyrifah selama 24 jam. Kami mengutamakan adab dalam kehidupan sehari-hari, jadwal ibadah tepat waktu, dan program hafalan Al-Qur'an setelah waktu shubuh dan ashar.
                            </div>
</div>
</details>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Contact CTA -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
<div class="bg-secondary-container rounded-xl p-10 lg:p-16 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-10 scroll-anim transition-all-custom">
<div class="space-y-4 text-center lg:text-left">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-on-secondary-container">Butuh Informasi Lebih Lanjut?</h2>
<p class="text-on-secondary-container opacity-90 max-w-lg">Tim Customer Service kami siap melayani pertanyaan seputar kurikulum, fasilitas, dan biaya operasional setiap hari kerja (08:00 - 16:00).</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
<button class="bg-secondary text-white font-bold px-8 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg hover:bg-[#6a4220] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="call">call</span>
                                Hubungi via WhatsApp
                            </button>
<button class="bg-on-secondary-container text-white font-bold px-8 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg hover:bg-[#5b3819] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="mail">mail</span>
